{"tid":2114703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍灣廣場阿信屋女收銀染疫","createTime":"2020-07-19T04:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T06:31:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2383fe460fafa9aaac7b3cef811b01695997a05c","tid":2114703,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200719/CHI4GGXLILGLF26UTNICXNACUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200719%2FCHI4GGXLILGLF26UTNICXNACUY%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=c3430772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200719%2FCHI4GGXLILGLF26UTNICXNACUY%2F&h=731bf294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200719/CHI4GGXLILGLF26UTNICXNACUY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n藍灣廣場阿信屋女收銀染疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z5P9LzUlD0ed2zvES9H0f34cK6A=/627x421/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FONSBR7NNUJZFS4RQ4VVZP6AI4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz5P9LzUlD0ed2zvES9H0f34cK6A%3D%2F627x421%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFONSBR7NNUJZFS4RQ4VVZP6AI4.gif&h=e066d243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小西灣藍灣廣場阿信屋分店一名女收銀員確診，店舖昨已停業。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨新增的本地確診個案有超過一半、共35宗源頭未明。當中包括小西灣藍灣廣場759阿信屋分店一名女收銀員，相信她在確診前曾接觸大量小西灣居民，有傳播病毒風險；而海關亦再有一名關員受感染，海關至今兩人確診。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心昨公佈，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場清潔工中招<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「港版火神山」擬接收輕症患者<br />\n<br />\n李鳳琼又指，該阿信屋分店是小西灣居民購物熱點，區內不少長者都喜歡到藍灣廣場行街。女患者負責收銀，有播毒風險。有消息稱女患者居於慈雲山，其家人亦已初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n其他源頭不明個案包括第1745號，是油麻地一名42歲男小販，平日接觸不少居民；第1754號為一名在機場客運大樓洗手間任清潔的71歲男子，有消息指他確診前曾使用客運大樓六樓近Gate 1的男洗手間及曾使用五樓近E1的機場員工休息室。<br />\n<br />\n海關亦再有人員確診，第1769號患者為關員，7月14日起咳嗽及發燒，而第1748號患者是他妻子，兩人居於黃大仙。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞報道，《南華早報》一名編輯昨初步確診，他上周一、二曾在時代廣場辦公室工作，辦公室昨晚關閉消毒。"},{"pid":"dce2e76ef2fb68aa4a5f2719f6a9e27c0a8793c8","tid":2114703,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"very good ball"}]}